                            Actionable Intelligence, When and Where You Need It                        


                            You won’t find one-size-fits-all products here. Our web-based platforms cater to the needs of specific market segments—needs determined by users like you. Turn raw data into actionable intelligence that’s critical to your workflow. And access it anywhere, via desktop, web, mobile, or datafeeds.
                        






Key Platforms







                                    SNL
                                

                    The SNL platform combines ground-floor information with the sector-specific metrics and analytics that are relevant to the industries we cover.
                


 Learn More                             





                                    S&P Cap IQ
                                

                    Boost your advantage and productivity with the S&P Capital IQ platform: your single source for a powerful array of financial data, analytics, and research.
                


 Learn More                             













Credit & Risk







                                 RatingsDirect®                             










                                 CreditPro®                             










                                 Credit Analytics                             










                                 Credit Assessment Scorecards                             










                                 Loss Given Default Models                             










                                 RatingsXpress on Xpressfeed™                             









RatingsDirect®

                        Magnify your view of the fixed-income markets across the globe with RatingsDirect®, offering credit ratings and research from S&P Global Ratings.
                    







 Find Out More  







CreditPro®

                        Enhance the rigor and veracity of your credit risk assessments by integrating rating transition matrices and default and recovery rates that are tailored to reflect your specific portfolio and risk management requirements.
                    







 Find Out More  







Credit Analytics

                        Credit Analytics on the S&P Capital IQ platform provides essential data, tools, and analytical models to help you stay one-step-ahead of credit risk.
                    







 Find Out More  







Credit Assessment Scorecards

                        S&P Global Market Intelligence’s Credit Assessment Scorecards provide credit and risk management professionals with the essential tools needed to identify and manage potential default risks of private, publicly traded, rated and unrated companies (obligors) of any size, across a multitude of sectors.
                    







 Find Out More  







Loss Given Default Models

                        Refine the assessment of your potential exposure to defaults with S&P Global Market Intelligence’s loss given default (LGD) models and scorecards.
                    







 Find Out More  







RatingsXpress on Xpressfeed™

                        You need the right data to make the right decisions, and you need to get it quickly. Spend more time conducting analysis and less on retrieving and managing credit ratings data with RatingsXpress on our powerful data feed management solution – Xpressfeed.
                    







 Find Out More  















Nothing satisfies us more than helping you complete a project or meet a deadline. Turn to our 24x7x365 global support team anytime, from anywhere. We're just a phone call or email away.

